(7237, 3151, 840, 3, 'Sea Rose', '', '2008-07-22 00:00:00', 0000, 15, 0, 3, 'Rose,harsh rose,\r\nMarred and with stint of petals.\r\nMeager flower,\r\nThin flower\r\nSparse of leaf.\r\n\r\nMore precious than a wet rose,\r\nSingle on a stem,\r\nYou are caught in the drift,\r\nYou are sea rose.\r\n\r\nStunted with small leaf,\r\nYou are flung on the sand.\r\nYou are lifted in the crisp sand that drives in the wind.\r\n\r\nCan the spice-rose drip such acrid fragrance,\r\nHardened in a leaf?\r\nYou are sea flower,sea rose\r\n', '', 292, '', '林笛', 'H.D', '胡戈', '水底音樂', '', 0, 0, 1, '2008-07-22 05:00:25', '2013-10-07 17:12:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7238, 3151, 840, 4, '淩晨三點', '', '2008-07-22 00:00:00', 0000, 15, 0, 4, '\r\n淩晨三點站在陽臺上看風景\r\n天上有人匆忙趕路背著手風琴\r\n懷裏溫軟的貓咪閉上了眼睛\r\n對面小學的工地上閃著綠光影\r\n\r\n傍晚的時候天上有很多雲\r\n飄來飄去的兔子，飛機和鯨魚\r\n有人在夜裏也曾向我提起\r\n嘿，你錯過了海豚真可惜\r\n\r\n十個月前我撿了一隻貓咪\r\n它喜歡在睡前咬我的手臂\r\n我忍著疼  聽它像我一樣歎氣\r\n現在它也喜歡  在陽臺上看風景\r\n\r\n時間流逝我還是一個孤魂\r\n沒有一個朋友沒有一個鬼魂\r\n夜晚抱緊了我也抱緊了我的貓咪\r\n它就是我下輩子要變成的東西\r\n\r\n某天路過那座墓碑一樣沈默的大樓\r\n看到有個人抱著貓在陽臺上看風景\r\n來生我將變成一隻貓\r\n在城市上空跳傘\r\n', '', 281, '', '林笛', '林笛', '林笛', '水底音樂', '', 0, 0, 1, '2008-07-22 05:12:03', '2013-10-07 17:12:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7239, 3151, 838, 1, 'Lumi Pumpuli', '林笛寫給死去的貓咪Lumi，願她在天堂安息。\r\n\r\n', '2008-07-22 00:00:00', 0000, 20, 0, 4, 'once upon a time, \r\nin the first blush of spring, \r\na tiny snowflake fell from heaven. \r\nwhen this magical snowflake landed on earth \r\nshe melted into the form of a white kitten. \r\neveryone who saw her was instantly charmed. \r\neven people on the other side of the world \r\n\r\nWho named her Lumi Pumpuli,\r\nWho feed her milk and fish\r\nwho built a little bed for her to sleep\r\nwho held her in their hand, \r\nwho felt happy ''cause she is purring\r\nwho laughed when she looked silly\r\nsuch was love''s design\r\n\r\n\r\nBut springtime snows do not last \r\nLumi had to return to heaven. \r\nwhen the tiny snowflake melted, \r\nshe left behind a pool of tears. \r\n\r\nlumi - wait for me in heaven\r\nmami will be there soon\r\nthere''s a tiny bright star in the night sky\r\nto the right of the lonesome moon\r\n\r\nLumi, Lumi are you there somewhere?\r\nLumi, Lumi can you come back home?\r\n\r\nLumi lumi wait for me in heaven\r\nLumi mami will be there soon\r\nthere''s a tiny bright star in the night sky\r\nshining to me like tear drops.\r\n\r\nWho can no longer call Lumi Pumpuli,\r\nwho can never touch little fish bowl?\r\nWho buried a little body under a tree\r\nWho won''t need to clean the paw print\r\nWho can’t smile at her pictures\r\nWho''s open eyes saw sun turn black\r\nwas such love''s design?\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nLumi Pumpuli on the way to heaven,\r\nwill she miss everything used to be given?\r\nIf there is no milk, fish, hug and kiss\r\nwill you run back to mami’s dream?\r\n\r\nclimb my leg,\r\npurr in my lap, \r\nlay by my head \r\nrolling by my side\r\njump on the table\r\nsteal my fish\r\nfollow me everywhere\r\nplay hide and seek\r\n\r\nsuch was love''s design\r\n', '', 303, '', '林笛', '林笛', '林笛', '水底音樂', '', 0, 0, 1, '2008-07-22 05:19:30', '2013-10-07 17:12:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7240, 3151, 839, 1, 'Perfect Ghost I', '', '2008-07-22 00:00:00', 0000, 20, 0, 4, 'I would like to be a falling cloud \r\nLanding gently by your side\r\nThe slightest wisp melted by your body heat.\r\n\r\nI would like to be the stars that you can see \r\nAny leaf you can hold in your mouth\r\nAny stone you can put in your pocket\r\nAny one you can meet on the street\r\n\r\nSince you walked into my secret garden\r\nI have become all too real\r\nIt seems I will never disappear\r\nI can come alive in anything\r\n\r\nI am the only god of my own world\r\ncrying in my cage day and night\r\nEvery day you save me on the brink of collapse\r\nEvery day you kiss my numb and frozen face\r\n\r\nOh, my perfect ghost\r\nNightly meet in a perfect dream\r\nOh, my perfect ghost\r\nAppear in the silent mirror\r\n\r\n\r\nSince you walked into my secret garden\r\nI have become all too real\r\nIt seems I will never disappear\r\nI can come alive in anything\r\n\r\n\r\nThis world is just as big as two hearts\r\nOne stops beating, and the other would die\r\nThis is the most beautiful result I believe\r\nStaring into each other''s dying eyes\r\n', '', 241, '', '林笛', '林笛', '林笛', '水底音樂', '', 0, 0, 1, '2008-07-22 05:21:18', '2013-10-07 17:12:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7241, 3151, 839, 2, 'Perfect Ghost II', '', '2008-07-22 00:00:00', 0000, 20, 0, 4, 'The roses you send still smell fragrant\r\nEven if withered… \r\nYou disappear for a while the world become stifling\r\nI am like a child abandoned in the desert of white\r\nWhat do I have to be proud of?\r\nI am just a lonely soul\r\n\r\nEven if you surround me with praise everyday\r\nI still hang in an endless void\r\nRising sun\r\nSetting sun\r\nAlone I sleep\r\nAlone I awake\r\nI do not know the meaning of life\r\nWithout you somewhere waiting\r\n\r\nRising sun\r\nSetting sun\r\nRising sun\r\nSetting sun\r\nRising sun\r\nSetting sun\r\nAlone I sleep\r\nAlone I awake\r\nI do not know the meaning of life\r\nWithout you somewhere waiting\r\n', '', 225, '', '林笛', '林笛', '林笛', '水底音樂', '', 0, 0, 1, '2008-07-22 05:24:38', '2013-10-07 17:12:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(7242, 3151, 840, 7, '很', '', '2008-07-22 00:00:00', 0000, 10, 0, 4, '一個人　還寂寞嗎\r\n一個人　可以跳舞嗎\r\n雲還飄　青絲怎麽繞\r\n落了多少\r\n\r\n一個人　還做夢嗎\r\n一個人　繼續演戲嗎\r\n夜風吹　扯起千般愁\r\n臉兒怎不皺\r\n\r\n想哭怕哭　想笑恨笑\r\n想到相識分離忘記\r\n難得很晚　難得很久\r\n難得想念一個忘了的人\r\n', '', 206, '', '林笛', 'Fly/林笛', '胡戈', '水底音樂', '', 0, 0, 1, '2008-07-22 05:39:06', '2013-10-07 17:12:52', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
